<div class="config-vars">
  <h3><a class="title-link" name="configuration-variables" href="#configuration-variables"></a> Configuration Variables</h3>
  <dl class=''><dt><a class='title-link' name='type' href='#type'></a> type</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Required)</span><span class='description'><p>entity</p>
</span></p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='entity' href='#entity'></a> entity</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Required)</span><span class='description'><p>Open Peer Power entity ID.</p>
</span></p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='name' href='#name'></a> name</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Optional)</span><span class='description'><p>Name of Entity</p>
</span></p><p class='default'>
Default value: <p>Entity Name</p>
</p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='icon' href='#icon'></a> icon</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Optional)</span><span class='description'><p>Overwrites icon.</p>
</span></p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='attribute' href='#attribute'></a> attribute</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Optional)</span><span class='description'><p>An attribute associated with the <code>entity</code></p>
</span></p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='unit' href='#unit'></a> unit</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Optional)</span><span class='description'><p>Unit of Measurement given to data</p>
</span></p><p class='default'>
Default value: <p>Unit Of Measurement given by entity</p>
</p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='theme' href='#theme'></a> theme</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='string'>string</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Optional)</span><span class='description'><p>Set to any theme within <code>themes.yaml</code></p>
</span></p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='footer' href='#footer'></a> footer</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='map'>map</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Optional)</span><span class='description'><p>Footer widget to render. See <a href="/lovelace/header-footer/">footer documentation</a>.</p>
</span></p></dd></dl>
</div>
<h2>Example</h2>
<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml">- type: entity
  entity: cover.kitchen_window
- type: entity
  entity: light.bedroom
  attribute: brightness
  unit: &#39;%&#39;
- type: entity
  entity: vacuum.downstairs
  name: Vacuum
  icon: &#39;mdi:battery&#39;
  attribute: battery_level
  unit: &#39;%&#39;</code></pre></figure>
